    "title": "Entry-Level Business Development Manager at Tata Housing",
    "description": "Tata Housing has an exciting opening for a Business Development Manager at our Aurangabad office. Join a company that values innovation, collaboration, and continuous learning.\n\nAbout Tata Housing:\nTata Housing is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Negotiate pricing, terms, and conditions on behalf of clients\n• Provide advisory services on property investment and market trends\n• Manage RERA documentation and compliance requirements\n• Coordinate with legal teams for documentation and title verification\n• Conduct site visits and property presentations for clients\n• Maintain a pipeline of qualified leads using CRM software\n• Source and close property deals with prospective buyers and investors\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Any graduate with relevant experience\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in GIS Tools\n• Proficiency in Property Valuation\n• Proficiency in Lease Administration\n• Proficiency in Contract Management\n• Proficiency in Project Management\n• Proficiency in Title Search\n• Proficiency in Market Research\n• Proficiency in Portfolio Management\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Learning & development budget\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Aurangabad, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Tata Housing!",
